{"tid":1155872,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱個frd話去買爭鮮外賣食，俾我屌到跪喺街度喊","createTime":"2019-05-15T08:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T09:39:11.000Z","uid":150100,"like":13,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5d393e831fe1f2ea3e3b78b2c178a2df6b967d48","tid":1155872,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我地一班大學friend就成日出街食飯嘅，唔係自助餐就放題，唔係放題就食西餐据牛排燒羊架，平均一餐2、300蚊走唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁講真，真係一啲都唔過份囉，話曬我地都係大學生，天之驕子嚟㗎嘛，唔通食啲100蚊都唔駛嘅垃圾咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係偏偏我地其中一個friend就成撚日呻窮，今日佢竟然話不如食爭鮮算啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：窮撚friend<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌你老母，竟然叫我地成班大學生食豬餿，上次買咗個爭鮮外賣返歸餵狗，連我屋企隻狗都唔撚食呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：但係我冇錢&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：冇錢唔識問老母攞？你啞定弱智？<br />\n<br />\n屌屌下我實在忍唔撚住<br />\n<br />\n你同我跪喺度！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條友又真係一嘢跪咗喺度，仲開始流埋馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我冇老豆老母㗎，屋企攞綜援㗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：冇錢就咪學人埋堆啦，躪返屋企食狗屎啦<br />\n<br />\n之後我就同班friend由得佢跪喺度走咗去食好西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：爭鮮狗也不屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我最中意食爭鮮"},{"pid":"660e4326d7e7eed15ada536fde4bcc1dddf87edd","tid":1155872,"uid":203714,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:44:16.000Z","msg":"又係你條on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c508ce264cf1390b83ccc7902e9e4d040067b8b","tid":1155872,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:44:27.000Z","msg":"屌，又唔記得紅色大字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5b2167d21936370c9080e1c5b5f04ce16431c1","tid":1155872,"uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:44:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你同我跪喺度！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5e8394abd51079b6367a3de5d8e77ca799630703","tid":1155872,"uid":251666,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:45:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ffff5c6e5a327cba0a08da217116c7bafef5b93","tid":1155872,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"660e4326d7e7eed15ada536fde4bcc1dddf87edd","tid":1155872,"uid":203714,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:44:16.000Z","msg":"又係你條on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:45:17.000Z","msg":"你就on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decb22b60925cd74e4ecd74273a62a1413d9dfac","tid":1155872,"uid":150100,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5e8394abd51079b6367a3de5d8e77ca799630703","tid":1155872,"uid":251666,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:45:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:46:07.000Z","msg":"佢人都走咗咯，唔好攞人啲嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd14f8bf3fa4752358df9c9b6fcc392c5b13d03","tid":1155872,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:47:14.000Z","msg":"原來連登咁多人中意食爭鮮"},{"pid":"1890505d1aaa8c200761a7d6365900d911e97930","tid":1155872,"uid":49275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor